基于实数矩阵的加法和乘法运算，可以在以下矩阵的集合
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathbb{C}:=\left\{ \begin{bmatrix}x & y\\
-y & x
\end{bmatrix}:x,y\in\mathbb{R}\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

 上定义加法和乘法运算
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\begin{bmatrix}x_{1} & y_{1}\\
-y_{1} & x_{1}
\end{bmatrix}+\begin{bmatrix}x_{2} & y_{2}\\
-y_{2} & x_{2}
\end{bmatrix} & :=\begin{bmatrix}x_{1}+x_{2} & y_{1}+y_{2}\\
-y_{1}-y_{2} & x_{1}+x_{2}
\end{bmatrix}\\
\begin{bmatrix}x_{1} & y_{1}\\
-y_{1} & x_{1}
\end{bmatrix}\cdot\begin{bmatrix}x_{2} & y_{2}\\
-y_{2} & x_{2}
\end{bmatrix} & :=\begin{bmatrix}x_{1}\cdot x_{2}-y_{1}\cdot y_{2} & x_{1}\cdot y_{2}+x_{2}\cdot y_{1}\\
-(x_{1}\cdot y_{2}+x_{2}\cdot y_{1}) & x_{1}\cdot x_{2}-y_{1}\cdot y_{2}
\end{bmatrix}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

其中，矩阵内的运算符表示实数域 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{R}$
\end_inset

 上的运算，括号外的运算符表示集合 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{C}$
\end_inset

